title: Shuffle Leadership
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: party_affairs
view-if: shuffle_leadership_timer = 0 and difficulty >= 0
on-arrival: month_activities += 1; shuffle_leadership_timer = 8;
card-image: img/shuffle.jpg
go-to: rm_main

Changing the leadership of the party is painful, but perhaps it is necessary to adapt to changing circumstances.

Removing advisors will increase dissent from their faction of the party, while selecting advisors will increase a faction's strength.

- @rm_main: Remove advisors
- @add_advisors: Add advisors
- @remove_none: Don't change advisors.
- @easy_discard


###################### removing leaders

@rm_main
title: Remove advisors.
tags: moderate_right_advisor, classical_liberal_advisor, social_liberal_advisor, christian_left_advisor, nonfactional_advisor 
frequency: 1

- #remove_advisor
- @add_advisors: Add advisors

@remove_none
title: Stop changing advisors.
go-to: root
tags: remove_advisor


# moderate right


@remove_reither
title: Remove Reither
view-if: reither_advisor
on-arrival: reither_advisor = 0; moderate_right_dissent += 5; n_advisors -= 1
tags: remove_advisor
go-to: rm_main

Reither has been removed as an advisor. The Moderate Right faction disapproves.


@remove_adamovich
title: Remove Adamovich
view-if: adamovich_advisor
on-arrival: adamovich_advisor = 0; moderate_right_dissent += 3; n_advisors -= 1
tags: remove_advisor
go-to: rm_main

Adamovich has been removed as an advisor. The Moderate Right faction disapproves.


# classical liberal


@remove_hayek
title: Remove Hayek
view-if: hayek_advisor
tags: remove_advisor
on-arrival: hayek_advisor = 0; classical_liberal_dissent += 5; n_advisors -= 1
go-to: rm_main

Hayek has been removed as an advisor. The Classical Liberal faction disapproves.


@remove_mises
title: Remove Mises
view-if: mises_advisor
tags: remove_advisor
on-arrival: mises_advisor = 0; classical_liberal_dissent += 3; n_advisors -= 1
go-to: rm_main

Mises has been removed as an advisor. The Classical Liberal faction disapproves.


# social liberal


@remove_kelsen
title: Remove Kelsen
