go-to: rm_main

Kelsen has been removed as an advisor. The Social Liberal faction disapproves.


# christian left


@remove_dobretsberger
title: Remove Dobretsberger
view-if: dobretsberger_advisor
tags: remove_advisor
on-arrival: dobretsberger_advisor = 0; christian_left_dissent += 5; n_advisors -= 1
go-to: rm_main

Dobretsberger has been removed as an advisor. The Christian Left faction disapproves.


## nonfactional


@remove_baade
title: Remove Baade
view-if: baade_advisor = 1
tags: remove_advisor
on-arrival: baade_advisor = 0; n_advisors -= 1
go-to: rm_main

Baade has been removed as an advisor.





####################### adding advisors

@add_advisors
title: Add advisors
choose-if: n_advisors < 3
unavailable-subtitle: Maximum of 3 advisors.
go-to: advisor_menu

@advisor_menu
title: Add other advisors.
tags: moderate_right_advisor, classical_liberal_advisor, social_liberal_advisor, christian_left_advisor, nonfactional_advisor
frequency: 1


- @moderate_right: Add Moderate Rightists
- @classical_liberal: Add Classical Liberals
- @social_liberal: Add Social Liberals
- @christian_left: Add Christian Leftists
- @nonfactional: Add non-factional advisors
- @rm_main: Remove advisors instead.
- @remove_none: Stop changing advisors.

@moderate_right
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #moderate_right_advisor

@classical_liberal
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #classical_liberal_advisor

@social_liberal
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #social_liberal_advisor

@christian_left
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #christian_left_advisor

@nonfactional
view-if: n_advisors < 3

- #nonfactional_advisor


# moderate right


@add_reither
title: Josef Reither
subtitle: WIP. {!<br><br>!}[? if difficulty < 0 : Actions - WIP ?]
is-card: true
face-image: img/portraits/ReitherJosef.jpg
tags: moderate_right_advisor
view-if: not reither_advisor and n_advisors < 3 and moderate_right_oclk
on-arrival: reither_advisor = 1; n_advisors += 1; moderate_right_strength += 5
go-to: advisor_menu

